{"tid":2227584,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"又要做雞，又要貞節牌坊系列⋯我係一個特務警察","createTime":"2020-10-03T01:59:39.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-03T02:25:32.000Z","uid":333488,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"e4b0729c0654db524d29916a5287bfc1fee6c6f3","tid":2227584,"uid":333488,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-03T01:59:39.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/CivilSecrets/posts/1051367258625724\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2FCivilSecrets%2Fposts%2F1051367258625724&d=ooVnpwewILBg1HoWGmAtmSWRWsFhQrZK9M853DAdSZ8%3D&h=5fd63b8e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/CivilSecrets/posts/1051367258625724</a><br />\n有感而發.....<br />\n10月1号終於過去社會常算平靜，我係一個特務警察(SC)，係9月30凌晨當值時比個朋友撞到，因當值地點係佢工作既地方，之後佢whatapp問我點解好好地自己份工唔做去做（動物）個個字太侮辱唔想講）走黎做看更，我只答佢一句，如果因為咁做唔到朋友咁就唔好做啦⋯⋯<br />\n<br />\n宜家特務警察大約有一千人左右黎至唔同既紀律部隊，我都有同其他SC傾過我相信我地既壓力唔會比警察小，我地如果比親人，朋友，其他本身既同事知道我哋唔可以只係話打份工遮搵食無計！<br />\n<br />\n我地SC只可以大大聲講我地係為社會為政府為警察，大家都知好多部門唔同警察部咁一條心，做緊SC既兄弟都話反回自己工作單位時都感受到一定既壓力！好似我地咁我地係要反訓練學院換衫既，曾經都有學仔影我地相，我地既OT又唔可以直接落局做，怕比自己同事知，因為真係太多唔同政見既同事，又會擔心比人杯葛，又會擔心比人地起底，平時又多多說話聽！<br />\n<br />\nSorry，容許我話句做SC大多數比警察更藍！有人話你怕又去做？我可以話係黑暴面前完全冇懼怕，只係怕身邊既屋企人要承受不必要嘅壓力.....<br />\n<br />\n唔好誤會我唔係博同情同呃like唔係話自己有幾偉大，我只係講好多同事既心聲。我地係想幫警察頂左一d後勸既位置，等佢地有多小小時間休息，多小小人手去前線守護我地香港......<br />\n<br />\n點都好香港警察加油後勤留反比我哋，當然如果可以同你地一齊並肩去前線就最好啦相信好多SC都係咁諗.....<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n有人唔做去做動物<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2bb966032e6fc494422ff4b292ce0be6d1109ebd","tid":2227584,"uid":51752,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-03T02:05:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"480fdd3e42aeda681d9f0c969f869b171f2f88b7","tid":2227584,"uid":123774,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-03T02:06:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/K8Mz6wO.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FK8Mz6wO.jpg&h=b59676cd&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"c8d2290a3c3bcf87b86c5f158a8ebedb4c87d815","tid":2227584,"uid":370061,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"480fdd3e42aeda681d9f0c969f869b171f2f88b7","tid":2227584,"uid":123774,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-03T02:06:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/K8Mz6wO.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FK8Mz6wO.jpg&h=b59676cd&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-03T02:11:04.000Z","msg":"皇家警察？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />呢啲人係依家狗隊應該冇錠企<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9b9d94dc4fed30b9130fa2201ea13439b01bf28b","tid":2227584,"uid":367007,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-03T02:25:32.000Z","msg":"Don&rsquo;t make stupid people famous<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}